My friend @xoalitaxo suggested that I try The Crème MSR-H . The Biologique Recherche Creme MSR-H contains a unique combination of ingredients, including wild yam extracts, soy extracts, shea butter, Vitamin E, and beeswax, as well as Biologique Recherche’s exclusive oxygen carrier. I apply this cream at night, and in the morning, my skin looks velvety, glowing, with less visible pores, and overall feels like I had an overnight facial. Although this cream is intended for mature skin, I believe it’s never too early to start preventing fine lines and wrinkles. The cream is intensely hydrating, and it leaves my skin feeling revitalized and balanced.

#biologiquerecherche @karinanycskincare
